The paper discusses the challenges of generating scalable data for big data benchmarking, which is closely related to the field of database systems (cs.DB) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The development of data generators also involves designing efficient algorithms and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also mentions generating text data and graph data, which are common in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG).
